    "description": "Explore a mysterious maze as the enigmatic FLUCTUOID, a lifeform that can change size.<br><br>Use your ability to shrink and grow at will to explore 9 different themed worlds, solving puzzles to explore further into the strange place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/5f1b3c14e42b7e1256ae6d7cc0a0104c.poster.avif?t=1677606900\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/5f1b3c14e42b7e1256ae6d7cc0a0104c.webm?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/5f1b3c14e42b7e1256ae6d7cc0a0104c.mp4?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Change size with the press of a button. When you're big you're heavy and slow but when you're small you're light and speedy<br></li><li>Slip through cracks in the maze by shrinking as you jump towards them<br></li><li>Grow big to sink deep into watery pools and explore hidden areas<br></li><li>Find a safe path between dangerous obstacles as time slows down the smaller you get</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/34bf865b60e383081918c8d06a9c9d13.poster.avif?t=1677606900\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/34bf865b60e383081918c8d06a9c9d13.webm?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/34bf865b60e383081918c8d06a9c9d13.mp4?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let the sounds relax you on your journey</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>FLUCTUOID starts easy but gets progressively more difficult<br></li><li>Don't let the challenge get to you, just take a breath and enjoy the soothing music<br></li><li>Try to collect all the mysterious cubes and change the ending you get</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/963efb222fbf1825674fb52e73ff6f0b.poster.avif?t=1677606900\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/963efb222fbf1825674fb52e73ff6f0b.webm?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287080/extras/963efb222fbf1825674fb52e73ff6f0b.mp4?t=1677606900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
